3030-003-000~belt, v-type~light duty, designed to fit evenly against the sides of pulley grooves, for fractional horsepower applications.  in determining the dimensions of most fhp belts by the size number, 3l320 means: "3l" indicates belt has nominal top width of "3/8" inches, "32" indicates belt is 32 inches long-outside circumference, "0" the last digit indicates additional tenths of an inch of length.  most belts are made in even inches and this digit will be zero.  "4l" indicates belt has nominal top width of 1/2 inch, "5l" indicates belt has nominal top width of 21/32 inches.
